<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Election Reminder</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #dddddd;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #333333;
    }
    p {
      color: #666666;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Election Reminder</h1>
    <p>Dear Voter,</p>
    <p>The election <strong>{{electionTitle}}</strong> has started and will end on <strong>{{electionEndDate}}</strong>.</p>
    <p>Please click the button below to cast your vote:</p>
    <a href="{{electionLink}}" class="btn">Vote Now</a>
    <p>Thank you for participating.</p>
    <p>Best regards,<br/>Election Committee</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
